      "text" : "Azure twinkles leave me breathless\nAs the dawn goes endlessly on",
      "title" : "Azure twinkles",
      "uuid" : "999DFF64-E541-4591-8096-949881B8B2CB"
    },
    {
      "eraUUID" : "955A02A6-3C2F-4604-8B43-6750E7CC1AB6",
